values:
Hello, I am Brittany. I am fourteen years old. I live in Ohio. I love afi,nirvana,and the misfits. I don't have many friends. I love the ones I have an I love making new ones. I'm pretty much online all the time. I like watching movies and hanging out with my friends. Music is my life I don't think I could live without it. I listen to a lot of different types of music. punk,metal,emo,ska,indie,rock,and death metal. Most of the info about me is in my userinfo. <3
Rules before you add me --1.Comment an tell me your adding me before you add me --2. If your going to add me comment on some of my entries --3. Update your journal once in a while so I know your alive --4. Do not type LiKe D1s It's annoying an I won't read it. --5. Do not start lj-drama with me or my friends. --6. Make sure we have at least one thing in common so I have a reason to add you --7. Please do not add me with out commenting first.
Love, Brit.
